Package: vscp
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description:This is a set of tools/a framework for M2M/IoT automation
 tasks such as home control (homeautomation) or environment monitoring.   
 The Very Simple Control Protocol can be used to automate 
 most equipment and the package VSCP & Friends contain tools
 to make this easy. The VSCP daemon can be used to set up
 automation environments. The VSCP Works graphical application 
 can configure, investigate and update firmware for remote nodes. A
 websocket interface and a built in webserver makes it very easy to create 
 lightweight user interfaces.
 More info at http://www.vscp.org


